title: Elton John - Love Songs [1996] DVD5
description: Elton John - Love Songs [1996] DVD5 Love Songs is a compilation album by British singer-songwriter Elton John. The album was first released on 6 November 1995 by John's own label The Rocket Record Company, in conjunction with Mercury Records. The release also spawned a music video compilation, which was originally released on laserdisc, VHS, and VCD.
